annotationA: Ribosomal protein L23A; Structural constituent of ribosome; nucleotide binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: translation; centrosome duplication; Belongs to the universal ribosomal protein uL23 family
annotationB: 60S ribosomal protein L7; Binds to G-rich structures in 28S rRNA and in mRNAs. Plays a regulatory role in the translation apparatus; inhibits cell-free translation of mRNAs (By similarity)
